    '[[$about-tab_expertise]]' => '<div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="tabs-4-1">                 
<h4>Our Expertise</h4>
                  <p>"Transkor" has been in business since 2002 and began developing and deploying its GLOBAL MTM method and tools at the oil&gas facilities in the Russian Federation in 2003. The initial focus was on pipeline mains but in 2004 the company initiated integrity checks of pipelines non-subject to in-line inspection. In 2005 the company began sourcing projects in other countries.</p>

<p>The company has executed over 60 projects since 2003 on multiple locations between USA and Australia.
In the year of 2006 its technology - in the form of joint-venture with PETRONAS (Malaysia) - was first applied for sub-sea pipelines in the South-China Sea and subsequently - in the Persian Gulf.</p>
<p>The GLOBAL MTM thechnology has been incessantly enhancing both in developing new techniques and modernization of the tools employed for pipelines integrity checks.</p>
<img src="img/workflow/map.png" alt="" width="835" height="418"/>
                </div>',
    '[[$about-tab_mission]]' => '                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="tabs-4-2">
