                  <p>We see the great potential in effective application of our own invention - GLOBAL MAGNETIC TOMOGRAPHY METHOD (GLOBAL MTM). We will further develop business in areas where Transkor is the market leader, but we\'ll also try to actualize full potential of our cutting-edge technology in other perspective fields.</p>
                  <img src="img/about/demands.jpg" alt="" width="835" height="418"/>
                </div>',
    '[[$about-tab_goals]]' => '<div class="tab-pane fade" id="tabs-4-3">
